Rules

"Suffix a Deletion in Vowel Final Stems"
!! __@RULENAME@__ gives maskwa + ak = plural maskwak
 Vx:0 <=> _ %>:0 :Vow ;
 	where Vx in ( a e i o â ê î ô ) ;

"w Insertion in Front of Vowel Initial Suffix after k and m"
!! __@RULENAME@__ inserts w after k, m in front of plural -ak
!! Note that this rule probably is wrong, and that the -w- is
!! a morphological affix rather than a phonological variant.
 0:w <=> [ k | m ] %>:0 _ a k ;
 
